  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><i>Is This a Platformer?</i> is a fast-paced action platformer that throws players into a hilariously absurd adventure filled with quirky characters, over-the-top obstacles, and laugh-out-loud moments at every turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of Kenzu, a young Japanese video game otaku, suddenly pulled into a bizarre digital world. His mission? Rescue his brother from the clutches of a mysterious creature in a universe where nothing makes sense—but everything is a challenge</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/07341fdbd0c34f293d28caf70f7d2f3c.poster.avif?t=1764778158\" width=374 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/07341fdbd0c34f293d28caf70f7d2f3c.webm?t=1764778158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/07341fdbd0c34f293d28caf70f7d2f3c.mp4?t=1764778158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Art Style:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Is This a Platformer?</i> brings its vibrant world to life with charming, retro-inspired pixel art. Think chunky, colorful pixels reminiscent of classic platformers but polished with modern touches. The result? A visual feast that blends nostalgia with fresh, creative flair.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And where else will you find a laughing sun or a bunch of screaming grapes? Oh, and don’t forget the explosive <i>Kaboom!</i> effect—because why not?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/9dbe7f2ce5a008db448759a99d5734ea.poster.avif?t=1764778158\" width=374 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/9dbe7f2ce5a008db448759a99d5734ea.webm?t=1764778158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/9dbe7f2ce5a008db448759a99d5734ea.mp4?t=1764778158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re just Kenzu—a regular guy with a killer jump and a mean punch. But in this world, <i>every</i> movement counts. Precision platforming, tight controls, and quick reflexes are your only allies as you leap, punch, and fight your way through absurd challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss fights? They're epic, over-the-top showdowns that mix intense platforming with wild humor and massive, unforgettable foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think you’ve got the skills to beat our toughest boss? Prove it. We dare you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/afecbd65a5a557c5790da5607a909e44.poster.avif?t=1764778158\" width=374 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/afecbd65a5a557c5790da5607a909e44.webm?t=1764778158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/afecbd65a5a557c5790da5607a909e44.mp4?t=1764778158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><i>Is This a Platformer?</i> is a fast-paced action platformer that throws players into a hilariously absurd adventure filled with quirky characters, over-the-top obstacles, and laugh-out-loud moments at every turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of Kenzu, a young Japanese video game otaku, suddenly pulled into a bizarre digital world. His mission? Rescue his brother from the clutches of a mysterious creature in a universe where nothing makes sense—but everything is a challenge</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/07341fdbd0c34f293d28caf70f7d2f3c.poster.avif?t=1764778158\" width=374 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/07341fdbd0c34f293d28caf70f7d2f3c.webm?t=1764778158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/07341fdbd0c34f293d28caf70f7d2f3c.mp4?t=1764778158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Art Style:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Is This a Platformer?</i> brings its vibrant world to life with charming, retro-inspired pixel art. Think chunky, colorful pixels reminiscent of classic platformers but polished with modern touches. The result? A visual feast that blends nostalgia with fresh, creative flair.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And where else will you find a laughing sun or a bunch of screaming grapes? Oh, and don’t forget the explosive <i>Kaboom!</i> effect—because why not?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/9dbe7f2ce5a008db448759a99d5734ea.poster.avif?t=1764778158\" width=374 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/9dbe7f2ce5a008db448759a99d5734ea.webm?t=1764778158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/9dbe7f2ce5a008db448759a99d5734ea.mp4?t=1764778158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re just Kenzu—a regular guy with a killer jump and a mean punch. But in this world, <i>every</i> movement counts. Precision platforming, tight controls, and quick reflexes are your only allies as you leap, punch, and fight your way through absurd challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss fights? They're epic, over-the-top showdowns that mix intense platforming with wild humor and massive, unforgettable foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think you’ve got the skills to beat our toughest boss? Prove it. We dare you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/afecbd65a5a557c5790da5607a909e44.poster.avif?t=1764778158\" width=374 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/afecbd65a5a557c5790da5607a909e44.webm?t=1764778158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919480/extras/afecbd65a5a557c5790da5607a909e44.mp4?t=1764778158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
